Case No. 8,873. McLAUGHLIN v. STELLE. [1 Cranch, C. C. 483.]1 Circuit Court, District of Columbia. June Term, 1808. [Cited in Hellrigle v. Dulaney, Id. 6,343.] ¡See Currey v. Fletcher [Case No. 3,490], Dec. term, 1802.

Courts — Jurisdictional Amount — Non Pros.

Assumpsit. Verdict for $11. Non pros.: it being below the jurisdiction of this court.
